casebody.data:
Yvette D. COTTON, Claimant-Appellant,
v.
EXPRESS EMPLOYMENT PROFESSIONALS, Respondent-Appellee,
and
Department of Talent and Economic Development/Unemployment Insurance Agency, Appellee. SC: 159039
COA: 338946 Supreme Court of Michigan. March 22, 2019

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the second motion of appellee Unemployment Insurance Agency to extend the time for filing its answer is GRANTED. The answer will be accepted as timely filed if submitted on or before April 2, 2019.
